    "isChapterStart": false,
    "type": "prose",
    "text": "The church had gone completely silent.\n\nEven the children stopped talking.\n\nEvery pair of eyes followed the man as he crossed the snow.\n\nHis boots left clear footprints behind him.\n\nThat somehow made it worse.\n\nWhatever he was...\n\nHe was still touching the ground."
