    "isChapterStart": false,
    "type": "prose",
    "text": "The man stopped.\n\nNot far from the church.\n\nClose enough that I could finally see his face clearly.\n\nHis smile hadn't changed once.\n\nNot a little.\n\nNot at all.\n\nIt looked...\n\nplaced there.\n\nLike someone had decided smiling was what people did.\n\nWithout understanding why."
