    "isChapterStart": false,
    "type": "prose",
    "text": "A chill crawled through me.\n\nNot from the cold.\n\nHe smiled.\n\nHe blinked.\n\nHe shifted his weight.\n\nEverything looked...\n\nalmost right.\n\nAlmost.\n\nExcept for one impossible detail.\n\nHe never breathed."
