    "isChapterStart": false,
    "type": "prose",
    "text": "That frightened me more.\n\nComplete silence.\n\nI walked toward one of the boarded windows.\n\nSamuel didn't stop me.\n\nI carefully looked through a narrow crack.\n\nThe man was gone.\n\nThe woods were empty.\n\nThe snow...\n\nLooked untouched.\n\nThen I noticed them.\n\nFootprints.\n\nHundreds.\n\nLeading away from the church.\n\nNot toward it.\n\nAway."
