    "text": "We pushed.\n\nThe church groaned around us.\n\nDust drifted from the ceiling.\n\nThe bell continued ringing.\n\nThe numbers on my arm changed faster than ever before.\n\n8:14.\n\n8:52.\n\n8:15.\n\n9:03.\n\n8:16.\n\nThen...\n\nThey stopped.\n\nFor the first time...\n\nThey became still."
